      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CROYDON (8) is in hot form with back to back wins at Broken Hill, running a dazzling 29.93 two back following up with 30.63 last time. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. PAW ZURI (3) turned in a better effort at Sandown last start, finishing third behind Secret Bandit (29.56) in a Special conditions H. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings five times from eight attempts. Bold showing expected. SCOTT SIGMA (7) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame from Box 2 last run (29.90) at Sandown. The form from her last run stacks up well. Overdue and expected to feature again. RALPH WIGGUM (2) generally performs well here at this distance.",
